Rules.InvariantScript:
If(
    JobContractInfoForm.FormMode = FormMode.Edit,
    Filter(
        JobContractInfoForm.LocationItems,
        fullAddress = JobContractInfoForm.Default.workLocation
    ),
    LookUp(
        JobContractInfoForm.LocationItems,
        primary
    )
)

If(
    IsMatch(
        JobContractInfoForm.Default.workingHours,
        $"Monday to Friday: \d\d:\d\d to \d\d:\d\d,( Saturday: \d\d:\d\d to \d\d:\d\d)?"
    ),
    JobContractInfoForm.PresentationData.WorkingHours.Options.Selector.Name,
    If(
        JobContractInfoForm.Default.workingHours = JobContractInfoForm.PresentationData.WorkingHours.Options.RotativeSchedules.Name,
        JobContractInfoForm.PresentationData.WorkingHours.Options.RotativeSchedules.Name,
        JobContractInfoForm.PresentationData.WorkingHours.Options.Custom.Name
    )
)
"Combines the character count of the 'Job activities' and 'Other job activities' fields"

{
    userADFI: Blank(),
    userHC: Blank(),
    workingHours: Blank(),
    extraJobActivities: Blank(),
    client: Blank(),
    workLocation: Blank(),
    compensationInLetter: Blank()
}

{ userADFI: { id: "c92f6789-7361-ee11-be6e-000d3a596548", name: "Florencia Alcain", role: "ADFI", email: "florencia.alcain@grupo-giga.com", idSystemUser: "850dc9da-dafd-ea11-a815-000d3a5988c5" }, userHC: { id: "87ada45c-7361-ee11-be6e-6045bd0064b3", name: "Paola Verdinelli", role: "Total Rewards", email: "paola.verdinelli@grupo-giga.com", idSystemUser: "c1fbc325-95e5-eb11-bacb-000d3a32deff" }, workingHours: "Monday to Friday: 08:00 to 17:30, Saturday: 08:00 to 13:30", extraJobActivities: "
  • Unirse al equipo de profesionales del rea.
  • Desarrollo de Software, soporte y seguimiento de las aplicaciones.
  • Desarrollo de procedimientos almacenados.
  • Desarrollo de aplicaciones WEB en plataforma .NET
  • Desarrollo de backend con tecnologas .NET, C#
  • Trato directo con usuarios y con el cliente.
", client: "Giga IT", workLocation: "Veracruz, Veracruz, Mxico", compensation: 20000 }

{
    userADFI: Self.ADFIUser.Value,
    userHC: Self.TotalRewardsUser.Value,
    workingHours: Self.WorkingHours.Value,
    extraJobActivities: Self.JobActivities.Value,
    client: Self.Client.Value,
    workLocation: Self.WorkLocation.Value,
    compensation: JobContractInfoForm.Default.compensation
}

IsEmpty(Warnings)
&& Self.ADFIUser.IsValid
&& Self.TotalRewardsUser.IsValid
&& Self.WorkingHours.IsValid
&& Self.JobActivities.IsValid
&& Self.Client.IsValid
&& Self.WorkLocation.IsValid
//&& Self.CompensationInLetter.IsValid
